    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tiny Kings is the whimsical medieval base builder where your dreams of building and managing a pint-sized kingdom come true! On top of that, you get to dominate a siege of tiny pesky enemies... if you don't die first!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205460/extras/65393ca420e282a0f29e88b25feee562.avif?t=1752973119\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your kingdom on a procedurally generated hexagon world, 'cause who wants to build realistically when you can build on hexagons! By the way builders like their vacation time, so you'll have to wait a couple of days to build again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205460/extras/07c90a9089588489846fff25024c7893.poster.avif?t=1752973119\" width=616 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205460/extras/07c90a9089588489846fff25024c7893.webm?t=1752973119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205460/extras/07c90a9089588489846fff25024c7893.mp4?t=1752973119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205460/extras/52df2ee94815ef8dd92731a181e19ddd.avif?t=1752973119\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the compassionate, yet bossy, ruler and assign your tiny citizens tasks to keep your kingdom fed and fighting. Or don't. eating is overrated anyway!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205460/extras/75cf49eea5c9402a4ba0e2a58292949f.poster.avif?t=1752973119\" width=616 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205460/extras/75cf49eea5c9402a4ba0e2a58292949f.webm?t=1752973119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205460/extras/75cf49eea5c9402a4ba0e2a58292949f.mp4?t=1752973119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205460/extras/2e19e23767436446367cd48746e9b151.avif?t=1752973119\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your precious little kingdom alive while all odds are against you! Yup, you guessed it, those pesky enemies are trying to take over your throne... again. Oh, don't forget about the changing seasons and possible arise of a crisis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205460/extras/ce823f93a6b1d0df34276d31cbc69e2f.poster.avif?t=1752973119\" width=616 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205460/extras/ce823f93a6b1d0df34276d31cbc69e2f.webm?t=1752973119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205460/extras/ce823f93a6b1d0df34276d31cbc69e2f.mp4?t=1752973119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards to show off your dominance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character customization so that your (puppet) king can look snazzy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Changing seasons and crisis for extra panic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedural hexagon world to build a  tiny kingdom in</p></li></ul>",
